code: public void testTuple() {     Tuple<Long, String> t1 = new Tuple<>(2L, "foo").     Tuple<Long, String> t2 = new Tuple<>(2L, "foo").     Tuple<Long, String> t3 = new Tuple<>(3L, "foo").     Tuple<Long, String> t4 = new Tuple<>(2L, "bar").     Tuple<Integer, String> t5 = new Tuple<>(2, "foo").     assertThat(t1.v1(), equalTo(Long.valueOf(2L))).     assertThat(t1.v2(), equalTo("foo")).     assertThat(t1, equalTo(t2)).     assertNotEquals(t1, t3).     assertNotEquals(t2, t3).     assertNotEquals(t2, t4).     assertNotEquals(t3, t4).     assertNotEquals(t1, t5).     assertThat(t1.toString(), equalTo("Tuple [v1=2, v2=foo]")). }
